User story 1

Airtraffic controller:

airport <- land(plane)
airport <- landed?(plane)

User story 2

Airtraffic controller:

airport <- take_off(plane)
airport <- departed?(plane)

User Story 3

Airtraffic Controller:

airport <- weather
airport <- take_off (raise error if)

User story 4

Air traffic controller

airport <- weather
airport <- land(plane -> raise error if)

User story 5

Air traffic controller
airport <- capacity
airport <-land -> raise error if full

User story 6

Air traffic controller
airport <- capacity -> raise error if full showing specified capacity